body:
Tests look green - all test failures here look unrelated.

This now builds on all platforms, with the caveat that the sorting is broken at runtime on windows (there are not tests for it on windows but sorting should be a no-op on windows).

@nicolasnoble and @jtattermusch, PTAL for the build changes here - probably especially the changes to the `Makefile.template`, bazel files, and `CMakeLists.txt.template`; these pass portability and artifact builds but definitely open to feedback for these :)
